# Bazel scaffolding — currently a PoC stub (every per-crate BUILD.bazel
# is comment-only, MODULE.bazel pinned to 0.5.7 while we're shipping
# 0.5.28). `bazel build //...` does not produce a working keyhog
# binary today; cargo is the real build system. Untracking until
# Bazel is fully wired and tested end-to-end, so we don't advertise a
# capability that doesn't exist.
